Task 4: AI-Powered Chatbot Using Cloud Computing 
Cloud-Based AI Chatbot for Customer Support
1. Introduction
Artificial Intelligence (AI) chatbots are software applications designed to simulate human conversation. They help users by answering questions instantly, reducing human workload, and providing 24/7 customer support.
This project develops a cloud-based AI chatbot capable of responding to user queries using predefined responses and AI-based processing.
The chatbot can be integrated into websites, educational portals, e-commerce platforms, and customer support systems.
2. Objective
The objectives of this project are:
Provide instant responses to users.
Reduce customer support workload.
Enable 24/7 availability.
Store conversation data in the cloud.
Improve user experience.
Demonstrate cloud-based AI application deployment.
3. Problem Statement
Organizations often face challenges such as:
Large numbers of customer queries.
Delayed responses.
High operational costs.
Limited support availability.
An AI chatbot can automatically answer common questions and provide continuous support.
